name: Alissa Violet
description:
A request of @463259395282.

Alissa Violet is an American model, actress and YouTuber.

This TI has been updated. Please check the "About this version" section below for more info on its training.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: Retrained from scratch after removing 3 pictures that I found "suspicious" of producing saturation. Trained for 1200 steps, which is unusually high for my latest embeddings, but it seems to have worked pretty well this time. Again, if you get saturated results, try reducing the embedding's weight in your prompt (for instance, "(alissav10l3t:0.99)"). Enjoy responsibly! :)

modelVersions.description: 300-step TI trained on a dataset of 20 images taken from her Instagram account. It's already producing slightly saturated results at this stage, so I suggest reducing the embedding's weight in your prompt. Try something like "(4lissaviolet:0.98)", see if the pics look better.
